{"000-section": {"000-title": "Green Urban Transport Scheme (GUTS)  to be Rolled Out in Urban Areas", "001-normal": "Under the Green Urban Transport Scheme (GUTS), the government would focus on creating non-motorized transport infrastructure, adoption of intelligent transport systems (ITS), increasing access to public transport, use of clean technologies and participation of private sector would be encouraged.", "002-normal": "The cities and urban areas where population is 5 Lakh or above are being considered for the implementation of the scheme.", "003-normal": "The initial investment of Rs. 25,000 crore by the central government would encourage private investment in allocating resources for GUTS for the next 5 years."}}